org.qbroker.persister

Class JMSPersister

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.persister.Persister
      • org.qbroker.persister.JMSPersister
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessagePersister

    public class JMSPersister
extends Persister
    JMSPersister listens to an XQueue and receives JMS messages from it. It puts the JMS Messages to a JMS Queue as the output. JMSPersister supports flow control and allows object control from its owner. It is fault tolerant with retry and idle options.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
